# Loovie Community reference server — model manifest.
#
# Tab-separated.  Lines starting with '#' are comments. Fields:
#   kind         : "image" or "video" — selected via LOOVIE_KIND.
#   hf_repo      : HuggingFace repo.
#   hf_filename  : path-in-repo.
#   target_subdir: ComfyUI folder name (diffusion_models, checkpoints,
#                  text_encoders, vae, loras, upscale_models, latent_upscale_models).
#
# Some entries are GATED on HuggingFace — accept the licence on the HF web
# UI while logged in before the download will succeed. See
# docs/25-huggingface-and-gated-models.md.
#
# These entries are best-effort against publicly-known repackaged repos
# (Comfy-Org/* primarily). If a download fails, verify the repo + filename
# on huggingface.co and update this manifest. Tracked in Part I as a
# launch checklist item.
#
# kind	hf_repo	hf_filename	target_subdir

# --- Image: FLUX.2 Klein (~7.75 GB) ----------------------------------------
image	Comfy-Org/flux2	flux-2-klein-4b.safetensors	diffusion_models
image	Comfy-Org/flux2	flux2-vae.safetensors	vae
image	Comfy-Org/flux2	qwen_3_4b_flux2.safetensors	text_encoders

# --- Video: LTX-2.3 fast (~36 GB) ------------------------------------------
video	Comfy-Org/ltx-2	ltx-2.3-22b-dev-fp8.safetensors	checkpoints
video	Comfy-Org/ltx-2	ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384.safetensors	loras
video	Comfy-Org/ltx-2	gemma_3_12B_it_fp8_scaled.safetensors	text_encoders

# --- Video pro tier: spatial upscaler + ESRGAN refiner (~2 GB) -------------
video	Comfy-Org/ltx-2	ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors	latent_upscale_models
video	xinntao/Real-ESRGAN	RealESRGAN_x2plus.pth	upscale_models
